{"tid":1165944,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經] 新牌買車","createTime":"2019-05-22T06:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T23:42:10.000Z","uid":130,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"92fdc74ad732d7b1201e790c8ff886d176b80746","tid":1165944,"uid":130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:31:50.000Z","msg":"上個月考到牌，想買架二手車仔代下步。<br />\n我都做過下功課，想買架Jazz，<br />\n不過仍有小小問題想問下。<br />\n因為打算屋企附近&amp;公司附近兩邊都放係露天爛地，<br />\n但上網睇D二手車盤多數都係有天窗, 擔心天窗會曬到溶, 之後漏水。<br />\n我呢個擔心合唔合理?<br />\n如果係我諗多左, 咁我揀盤就會好揀小小。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有其他建議? <br />\n例如Jazz既咩型號, EX / DELUXE (其實都唔知有咩分別)  會好D or 適合D?<br />\n或者其他車型提議? <br />\n我目的都係代步, AT, 車仔細細, 最好唔好普通嗰D四門房車 (civic) , 覺得感覺好老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。(我26歲)<br />\n筆直: 3皮"},{"pid":"8211cbd8f538cb676a5ad95e9894f4ecb682df26","tid":1165944,"uid":1621,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:47:13.000Z","msg":"係到問得啲人實係答你ae110"},{"pid":"af367a82cc4b0d27d85f86dd6da5b55e053834e4","tid":1165944,"uid":193421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"大把Jazz泊露天場日曬雨淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54891af649ece83fad2401189e25e19b441af520","tid":1165944,"uid":59001,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:01:20.000Z","msg":"Kia morning幾好 我自己都渣緊"},{"pid":"a461ed178a152495e7999bf5978a79ac1e7db052","tid":1165944,"uid":172244,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161127/photo/bkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001_01p.jpg?20161128095201\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161127%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20161128095201&h=fafbbec0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bf1e690dbfd35792ef72b6ebd156cb778760c68","tid":1165944,"uid":130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco